When SuppressDescription is used with the HTMLTable option the table header is
suppressed properly but extra empty cells are added to every row - the following
fixes the problem

--- mod_autoindex.c	Thu Apr 19 20:44:33 2007
+++ mod_autoindex.c	Thu Apr 19 20:49:01 2007
@@ -1733,9 +1733,9 @@
                                                         desc_width), NULL);
                     }
                 }
-            }
-            else {
+				else {
                 ap_rputs("</td><td>&nbsp;", r);
+				}
             }
             ap_rputs("</td></tr>\n", r);
         }


the else just needs to go inside the SUPPRESS_DESC check

Thanks!
